Content: we need to fork to enable sapling anyway

Content: the plan is for there to be a special rpc call you do that will be like z_mergetoaddress, or maybe it is just built into it, where it would do the last oldz -> tmptaddr, and tmptaddr -> new zaddr

Content: so on the blockchain there will be this flurry of the onetime used taddr and then all back to sapling z

Content: in order to not leak info (by whether you have or havent converted), we might make it an automatic and mandatory process to sync to the new fork
